Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:06.01,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,By January 1986, the Space\NShuttle had
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:07.42,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,flown twenty-four times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:08.82,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Each flight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:11.36,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,reinforced one idea the\Nsystem worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:14.94,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Across those flights,\Nengineers documented
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.72,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,O-ring damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:18.50,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Erosion, blow-by hot gas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:20.92,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,past seals designed to\Nhold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:23.88,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Low-temperature flights\Nall showed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:25.05,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:26.21,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,But each flight survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:28.07,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,and the warning lost\Nforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:30.74,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Danger became a known\Ncondition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:33.38,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,A stop signal became a\Nline item.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:36.47,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The night before\NChallenger, engineers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:38.00,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,recommended against\Nlaunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:39.53,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The burden
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:42.26,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,shifted instead of proving\Nit safe to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:44.59,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,fly, they were asked to\Nprove it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:46.37,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,was unsafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:48.15,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,On the coldest morning the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.80,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,program had ever faced,\Nseventy-three
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:52.09,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,seconds was all the\Nphysics needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.35,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,The warning was never\Nmissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:56.93,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,It had been made\Nsurvivable for too
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:58.73,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:00.53,DocumentaryLowerThird,,0,0,0,,Small causes, massive\Nconsequences.
